text: Hawaii Five-0 is a drama that first aired on September 20, 2010 on CBS, and is based on the original series. On May 15, 2011, the series was renewed for a second season, which premiered on September 19, 2011. The series ended on April 3, 2020. ==References== == Other websites == * * * * Category:2010s American drama television series Category:CBS network shows Category:2010 American television series debuts Category:English-language television programs
